{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"","closed_at":null,"closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"897c979210a561c9d6768ceae1cbb6d5d85b0bb9e238353734d0a42ad9bf7130","created_at":"2026-03-03T14:23:45Z","created_by":"houxinyue","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"## 今日工作总结 (元宵节)\n\n### ✅ 已完成的工作\n\n#### 1. 前后端接口联调 (fusion-mark-39y)\n**目标**: 前端页面与后端API接口适配\n\n**修复内容**:\n- 修复前端 submitTask 字段名：pdf_url → document_url\n- 启用真实API调用，替换模拟处理流程\n- 完善WebSocket消息处理，支持进度更新\n- 添加任务失败状态处理\n\n**涉及文件**:\n- \frontend/src/app.js - 添加 submitTask, connectWebSocket, handleWebSocketMessage\n- \frontend/src/styles/main.css - 添加 .step.failed 样式\n\n#### 2. 错误提示修复\n**问题**: MinerU API Key 认证失败时页面一直等待，无错误提示\n\n**修复**:\n- 后端 (\u0007pi_server.py):\n  - 修复WebSocket回调协程问题，使用 \u0007syncio.run_coroutine_threadsafe\n  - 添加API Key前置检查\n  - 完善错误日志输出\n  \n- 前端 (\frontend/src/app.js):\n  - 添加 handleTaskFailed() 函数统一处理失败状态\n  - WebSocket连接时检查任务状态\n  - 添加红色失败样式\n\n#### 3. 422 URL格式错误修复\n**问题**: Pydantic HttpUrl 对某些URL验证过于严格\n\n**修复**:\n- 将 document_url 从 HttpUrl 改为 str\n- 添加自定义URL验证器\n- 支持更宽松的URL格式\n\n#### 4. 分阶段进度系统重构\n**问题**: 进度条跳跃，各阶段状态显示不清晰\n\n**新设计**:\n`json\n{\n  stage: mineru/extraction/highlight,\n  stage_progress: 0-100,\n  overall_progress: 0-100,\n  mineru: {state: running, progress: 45, logs: []},\n  extraction: {state: pending, progress: 0, ...},\n  highlight: {state: pending, progress: 0, ...}\n}\n`\n\n**进度分配**:\n- MinerU 解析: 40% (0-40%)\n- 实体提取: 30% (40-70%)\n- 高亮渲染: 30% (70-100%)\n\n**后端修改** (\u0007pi_server.py):\n- 重构 create_task 进度数据结构\n- 重写 process_pdf_task 使用分阶段进度\n- 添加 update_stage() 辅助函数\n\n**前端修改** (\frontend/src/app.js):\n- 添加 updateProgressByStage() 函数\n- 步骤状态映射 (extraction → extract)\n- 阶段进度实时显示\n\n### ⚠️ 遗留问题 (已记录)\n\n| ID | 问题 | 优先级 | 状态 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| fusion-mark-b6y | PDF预览显示翻转 | P1 | 待修复 |\n| fusion-mark-0ur | 进度条显示优化 | P2 | 待优化 |\n| fusion-mark-csy | LangExtract异步进度 | P1 | 调研Celery |\n\n### 📊 今日修改统计\n\n- **后端文件**: \u0007pi_server.py (+500行)\n- **前端文件**: \frontend/src/app.js (+200行), \frontend/src/styles/main.css (+10行)\n- **修复Bug**: 4个\n- **新增功能**: 分阶段进度系统\n- **创建Issue**: 3个\n\n### 🔧 技术要点\n\n1. **WebSocket异步处理**: 使用 \u0007syncio.run_coroutine_threadsafe 在主事件循环中安全发送消息\n2. **后台任务进度**: BackgroundTasks中通过共享队列/回调机制向前端推送进度\n3. **分阶段设计**: 每个阶段独立0-100%进度，便于后续添加详细日志\n\n### 📝 后续计划\n\n1. 调研 Celery + Redis 实现真正的异步任务进度\n2. 修复PDF.js渲染方向问题\n3. 优化前端UI/UX\n4. 文件上传功能（等待存储方案）","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"fusion-mark-4wb","is_template":0,"issue_type":"task","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"houxinyue18@outlook.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":1,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"open","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"工作总结: 2026-03-03 前后端联调","updated_at":"2026-03-03T14:23:45Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
